  <!-- EN: psychic bonding -->
  <PsychicBonding.label>心灵伴侣</PsychicBonding.label>
  <!-- EN: Carriers of this gene have a special neural organ that makes them psychically bond with a lover for life. Depending on the characteristics of the bonded individuals, they will receive unique effects as long as they are together. If they are physically separated, they will be disturbed by the distance. If one dies, the other's mind will be badly disrupted. -->
  <PsychicBonding.description>这种基因的携带者长有一特殊的神经器官，使得其在灵魂上可与爱人建立维系终生的纽带。根据双方所具有的特性，只要两个人在一起，就都会获得额外的独特加成，如果他们被物理上分开，则依据距离获得心情减益。如果其中一个死亡，存活者的思维将被严重扰乱。</PsychicBonding.description>
  
</LanguageData>